        <p class="comment-detail">Posted on: date</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="comment">
      <div class="comment-image">
        <img src="http://placehold.it/400x400" alt="Logo image">
      </div>
      <div class="comment-content">
        <a href='../../profile/index.html'<h1>Some Person has commented...</h1></a>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Optio, aspernatur, quia modi minima debitis tempora ducimus quam vero impedit alias earum nemo error tenetur sed.</p>
        <p class="comment-detail">Posted on: date</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%=# erb :'partials/pagination' %>

  </article>

</section>s


